These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, collecting, skydiving, baking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, superhero, sports
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, volleyball, skateboarding, sailing
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, roller, helicopter, skateboard
 1. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the right of the person who's sport is baseball##8
 2. the person driving the bus is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8
 3. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is not to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##8
 5. the person driving the bus is not to the right of the person driving the bus##8
 6. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 7. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
 8. the person watching sports movies is between the person driving the roller and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
 9. the person driving the skateboard is the person watching superhero movies##1
10. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
11. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
12. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
13. the person watching superhero movies is not to the left of the person driving the skateboard##8
14. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person driving the helicopter##1
15. the person who's hobby is collecting is not the person who's sport is volleyball##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | hiking     | collecting   | baking | skydiving |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | sports   | action   | superhero  |
| Sport         | volleyball  | skateboarding  | sailing  | baseball |
| Transport     | bus    | helicopter | roller     | skateboard    |

