.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice, tea, coffee
There 4 different types of food: radish, cucumber, strawberry, cauliflower
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, blues, gospel, jazz
4 different pets are kept: pony, cat, mouse, turtle
 1. the fan of gospel is between the owner of the pony and the fan of blues##2
 2. the person drinking juice is not to the right of the owner of the cat##8
 3. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the right of the owner of the turtle##8
 5. the owner of the pony is not to the left of the fan of blues##8
 6. the person eating cauliflower is not to the right of the person drinking coffee##8
 7. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5
 8. the owner of the mouse is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of ambient is the owner of the cat##1
10. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
11. the owner of the pony is not to the left of the fan of gospel##8
12. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
13. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the right of the person eating cucumber##5
14. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
15. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person eating radish##1
17. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the right of the fan of blues##8
18. the person eating cucumber is not to the right of the owner of the cat##8
19. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | tea | coffee  | juice  |
| Food          | cauliflower     | cucumber | radish | strawberry  |
| Music-Genre   | blues    | gospel  | jazz | ambient |
| Pet           | mouse | turtle | pony    | cat  |

