.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, collecting, writing, singing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, thriller, satire, horror
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, r&b, soul, classical
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, lacrosse, ice-hockey, baseball
 1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 2. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##5
 3. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5
 4. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the right of the fan of country##5
 5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the right of the person watching romance movies##8
 6. the person who's hobby is singing is not to the left of the person watching satire movies##8
 7. the fan of soul is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
 9. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
10. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far right##1
11. the person watching romance movies is not to the left of the fan of r&b##8
12. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | gardening    | singing   | writing | collecting |
| Movie-Genre   | romance     | satire  | horror   | thriller      |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | country    | soul      | classical       |
| Sport         | ice-hockey    | skateboarding | baseball   | lacrosse    |

