.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-4::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, grapefruit, carrot, mango
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, baking, singing, sudoku
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, engineer, dressmaker, bartender
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, handball, cycling, rugby
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is not the journalist##6
 2. the bartender is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
 3. the person eating mango is the dressmaker##1
 4. the person eating grapefruit is between the journalist and the engineer##2
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
 6. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the right of the person eating grapefruit##8
 7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
 9. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the bartender##1
10. the engineer is the person who's sport is swimming##1
11. the person who's sport is handball is not to the right of the person eating asparagus##8
12. the journalist is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
13. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
14. the engineer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
15. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Food    | carrot    | grapefruit             | asparagus   | mango     |
| Hobby   | drawing | singing            | sudoku | baking    |
| Job     | engineer | bartender | journalist  | dressmaker |
| Sport   | swimming  | handball               | cycling  | rugby   |

