The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, skateboarding, tennis, ice-hockey
 1. the person watching superhero movies is not to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##8
 2. the thai is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not the person who's hobby is traveling##6
 4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
 5. the person watching superhero movies is not to the right of the canadian##8
 6. the person who's sport is tennis is not to the right of the person watching superhero movies##8
 7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##8
 8. the colombian is the person watching documentary movies##1
 9. the brazilian is not to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##8
10. the person watching horror movies is not to the left of the person watching superhero movies##8
11. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person watching documentary movies##2
12. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
13. the colombian is not to the right of the person watching documentary movies##8
14. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
