.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, fanta, lemonade, almond-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, accountant, electrician, software-developer
There are 4 different nationalities: german, russian, brazilian, american
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, airplane, car, snowmobile
 1. the person driving the car is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
 2. the person driving the bike is not to the left of the software-developer##8
 3. the person driving the bike is not to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##8
 4. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
 5. the person driving the car is the brazilian##1
 6. the person drinking juice is not to the right of the russian##8
 7. the person drinking fanta is not the american##6
 8. the accountant is somewhere between the person driving the car and the person drinking fanta##7
 9. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the accountant##5
10. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the accountant##3
11. the electrician is on the right of the paramedic##1
12. the accountant is not the german##6
13. the russian is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
14. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
15. the person driving the bike is not to the right of the accountant##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | fanta    | almond-milk   | lemonade        | juice  |
| Job           | software-developer     | accountant | paramedic | electrician  |
| Nationality   | german | american    | brazilian   | russian     |
| Transport     | snowmobile       | bike     | car    | airplane |

