 4. the canadian is not the fan of salsa##6
 5. the fan of house is not to the left of the fan of r&b##8
 6. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
 7. the canadian is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the right of the owner of the rat##8
 9. the fan of r&b is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the fan of jazz##7
10. the fan of r&b is not to the left of the american##8
11. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the left of the french##5
12. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the right of the fan of house##8
13. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
14. the fan of house is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
