.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, almond-milk, mirinda, 7up
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, magic-tricks, woodworking, filmmaking
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, coach, analyst, lawyer
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, helicopter, subway, ship
 1. the coach is on the left or right of the lawyer##3
 2. the person driving the van is not the person who's hobby is baking##6
 3. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is baking##5
 4. the analyst is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 5. the person drinking mirinda is in an even position##4
 6. the person driving the ship is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking almond-milk##7
 7. the person driving the ship is not to the left of the person driving the subway##8
 8. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##7
 9. the freelancer is on the far left or far right##3
10. the coach is not to the left of the coach##8
11. the freelancer is on the far left##1
12. the lawyer is on the far right##1
13. the person driving the ship is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
14. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##8
15. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5
16. the coach is not to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4       |
| Beverage    | almond-milk        | soy-milk      | 7up      | mirinda          |
