.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, hot-chocolate, juice, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, indie, rock, pop
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, soccer, skiing, badminton
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, bus, skateboard, motorbike
 1. the person drinking juice is the person who's sport is badminton##1
 2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person driving the motorbike##5
 4. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
 6. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 8. the person driving the bus is not to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##8
 9. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
11. the fan of rock is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person driving the motorbike is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of rock is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | lemonade   | soy-milk     | juice    | hot-chocolate |
| Music-Genre   | house  | pop      | rock     | indie     |
| Sport         | baseball | skiing  | badminton     | soccer  |
| Transport     | subway     | skateboard | motorbike | bus     |

