 7. the lawyer is not to the right of the person driving the skateboard##8
 8. the librarian is on the far right##1
 9. the bartender is not to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##8
10. the person driving the trike is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5
12. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5
