 9. the fan of disco is in an even position##4
10. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
11. the person watching time-travel movies is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the paramedic and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
13. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left or far right##3

